From 42a6cd6143dea8b43d80d7496bd815b5c51079d8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: air-codex <aircodexyz@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 10:30:46 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Add secret leak detection guard (SEC-12)

Pre-commit guard that scans for hardcoded secrets and credentials in source code.
Covers 100+ patterns including API keys, connection strings, private keys, and
bearer tokens. Supports staged file scanning, full project audit, security grading,
and external scanning without leaving residues.

Constraint: Must integrate with VibeGuard existing guard structure
Rejected: Copy all scripts from credentials-guard | Scripts were project-specific,
not portable to VibeGuard structure
Confidence: high
Scope-risk: narrow
Reversibility: clean
Directive: Add data/reports/ to .gitignore to prevent committing scan reports
Tested: bash tests/unit/test_secret_leaks.sh (13/13 passing)
Not-tested: Integration with VibeGuard pre-commit-hook flow
